{"tid":1912394,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解香港獨立先係唯一出路？","createTime":"2020-03-06T04:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T21:54:58.000Z","uid":174174,"like":42,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5c0bb9ebc55039a7c2d56aa0d2dd0e907d7f9fed","tid":1912394,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:43:52.000Z","msg":"【文：三木真黒】 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/btHpLHp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbtHpLHp.jpg&h=c791ad12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要論點：<br />\n1. 好處：善用而家香港可以攬炒大陸經濟嘅籌碼，獲取最大嘅經濟政治利益，得到世界認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.  原因：唔獨立就唔會有制衡政府嘅權力\b產生<br />\n香港作為文明社會，需要有制衡政府、軍警嘅憲政，先至可以保障以後香港嘅穩定。當政府違憲時，人民大可以用選票推翻政府，而無須用武力解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但而家中國向來視憲法為保護黨利益、對付人民嘅工具，視任何制衡力量為推翻。而且，喺一國兩制嘅框架下，政府違憲都唔會有任何責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://medium.com/@highighig3/%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%94%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%87%BA%E8%B7%AF-9676d26220b3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40highighig3%2F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%2589%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2594%25AF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25B7%25AF-9676d26220b3&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=3fe3406c\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@highighig3/%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%94%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%87%BA%E8%B7%AF-9676d26220b3</a>"},{"pid":"0049a1d7b7b9aeab12c98d083fb4fc8d5a5dbedb","tid":1912394,"uid":223647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:44:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"feac6319960c6729f5120018f92fe56c025c8879","tid":1912394,"uid":223647,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:44:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4de7e9ff97ea76fb156e14feee15dcec7b3139f0","tid":1912394,"uid":329927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:48:26.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"95850e8852865e789ba7894b95cc9b95483c34f9","tid":1912394,"uid":174174,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"「唯一出路」呢四個字，本來係用嚟提醒同路人，唔好奢想喺殖民傀儡下，可以爭取到五大訴求<br />\n亦都係建基於眼見嘅政治現實之上，而無意抹殺其他本土論述<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ce67dd8a7f6269d65136dd8eec29cc40a1564c","tid":1912394,"uid":343189,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:52:27.000Z","msg":"亨利(無神論者巴別塔)老婆係警察,手足小心"},{"pid":"eda29978cd0272af50fb87ac0c92866056900b22","tid":1912394,"uid":292497,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e6ce67dd8a7f6269d65136dd8eec29cc40a1564c","tid":1912394,"uid":343189,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:52:27.000Z","msg":"亨利(無神論者巴別塔)老婆係警察,手足小心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:54:34.000Z","msg":"你係一個白板ac 手足小心"},{"pid":"2c2ef14a20820302a2e8e9afe9c39d2c0fad1e9e","tid":1912394,"uid":216776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"一直停留起論述階段"},{"pid":"fbc402472c440ca5504d0bc87ebf59be82a6c651","tid":1912394,"uid":343189,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eda29978cd0272af50fb87ac0c92866056900b22","tid":1912394,"uid":292497,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e6ce67dd8a7f6269d65136dd8eec29cc40a1564c","tid":1912394,"uid":343189,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:52:27.000Z","msg":"亨利(無神論者巴別塔)老婆係警察,手足小心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:54:34.000Z","msg":"你係一個白板ac 手足小心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:55:44.000Z","msg":"講得好,防人之心不可無!"},{"pid":"f5de1ae1572988fdaa6c22977b5f7082556cb447","tid":1912394,"uid":174174,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c2ef14a2082